Nivolumab versus chemotherapy in patients with advanced oesophageal squamous 
cell carcinoma refractory or intolerant to previous chemotherapy (ATTRACTION-3): 
a multicentre, randomised, open-label, phase 3 trial.

Kato K(1), Cho BC(2), Takahashi M(3), Okada M(4), Lin CY(5), Chin K(6), Kadowaki 
S(7), Ahn MJ(8), Hamamoto Y(9), Doki Y(10), Yen CC(11), Kubota Y(12), Kim 
