Brain metastases from cervical cancer reduce longevity independent of overall 
tumor burden.

Takayanagi A(1), Florence TJ(2)(3), Hariri OR(4)(5), Armstrong A(6), Yazdian 
P(7), Sumida A(8), Quadri SA(9), Cohen J(5), Tehrani OS(10).

Author information:
(1)Department of Neurosurgery, Riverside University Health Systems, Moreno 
Valley, USA.
(2)Department of Neurosurgery, Columbia University College of Physicians and 
Surgeons, New York, USA.
(3)Department of Neurosurgery, University of California Los Angeles, Los 
Angeles, USA.
(4)Department of Neurosurgery, Stanford University School of Medicine, Stanford, 
USA.
(5)Department of Neurological Surgery, Kaiser Permanente Orange County, Anaheim, 
